  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">In triangle <span class=\"italic\">ABC</span>, the measure of angle <span class=\"italic\">A</span> is <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"50 degrees\"></span></span>. If triangle <span class=\"italic\">ABC</span> is isosceles, which of the following is NOT a possible measure of angle <span class=\"italic\">B </span>?</p>\n",
